BBC 2 HD 30th Nov 2014
12:20pm to 1:20pm Highlights

Gabby Logan presents highlights from England's clash with Australia at Twickenham. Stuart Lancaster's side will be desperate to issue a statement of intent against the Wallabies, one of their opponents in next year's World Cup pool stages. Twickenham will host that crucial Pool A clash next October and the home faithful will be willing England to round off their autumn international campaign in style. Commentary comes from Andrew Cotter, Brian Moore and Mike Tindall.
